synopsis: Koko grows up in the jungle with a solitary Zarude. When he meets Ash and Pikachu, he discovers the human world — and a plot threatening his home!

name: Death Can Wait

name: My Village People
synopsis: A selfish womanizer finds himself in bubbling hot water after his reckless lifestyle accidentally attracts the attention of a coven of witches.

name: Home2Home
synopsis: In this documentary, a young man with a taste for adventure bikes 27,000 miles around the world and encounters people from all walks of life.

name: TIGER & BUNNY - The Rising -

synopsis: This action-adventure follows the exploits of 47 samurai warriors who plot to exact revenge on a court official responsible for their master's death.

synopsis: Every day is extraordinary for five doctors and their patients inside a hospital, where birth, death and everything in between coexist.

synopsis: Facing the death penalty for having murdered her lover’s lover, a young woman reflects on the tragic romance that triggered her actions.

name: The Main Event

name: The Road to Salina

synopsis: After his transfer to a suburban post, Inspector Léonetti and his assistant take on a difficult mission: finding the main witness in a criminal case.

synopsis: Filmed over 13 years, this real-life thriller follows the unprecedented story of two men accused of a grisly crime they may not have committed.

name: Edgar Rice Burroughs' Tarzan and Jane

name: Operation Leopard

name: Teen Wolf
synopsis: An animal bite turns a high schooler into a werewolf whose newfound supernatural abilities make him a star athlete – and majorly complicate his life.

name: The New Legends of Monkey

name: Gigantosaurus

name: Rugal

name: A Tale Dark & Grimm

name: The Decline
synopsis: An accident at a remote training camp leaves a group of survivalists bitterly divided — and caught in a brutal fight for their lives.

name: Dhh
synopsis: Convinced only a miracle can save them from failing school exams, a trio of friends seek help from a magician. To their surprise, he gamely complies.

synopsis: From road rage to couples fighting during the pandemic, comic Ricardo Quevedo examines the absurdity of the situations that try our patience.

name: Toxic Love
synopsis: A young man racks up a series of disastrous first dates, until he spends the night with an unconventional young woman who upends his life.

name: Pinocchio

name: The Doll 2
synopsis: A mother uses her deceased daughter’s doll as a medium to communicate with her, but the consequences are chilling. The second of the “Doll” films.

name: Clark

name: The Witcher Bestiary Season 1, Part 2

name: Howl’s Moving Castle

name: Captain Underpants Epic Choice-o-Rama

name: Monster Island

name: Masaba Masaba

name: In Good Hands

name: Teen Titans Go!

name: Father Christmas Is Back

name: Star Trek: The Next Generation

name: Beyblade Burst Surge

name: The Big Show Show

name: Diablero
synopsis: When a young girl goes missing in a big city, a desperate priest joins a demon hunter and his motley crew on an otherworldly mission to find her.
